_sText:
This map is updated from a previous version, different name, mostly for a smaller filesize.
--Also includes minor changes to avoid exploitation.

This map includes human cannons that shoot players across the map.

At the same time, defend yourself in castle barricades and snipe those coming across in cannons.

Perfect for short range weapons, long range weapons, knifing and hegrenades.

This map also has buy-zones for anyone who wishes to have this on any non-gungame server.

All textures created by myself.

Skybox texture credit goes to Karatek√§fer, thanks a bunch man, your skybox textures and soo amazing!

Note: your server physics will affect the cannons! Be wary!
